{"tid":2059873,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 突發 ] 無良奸商！ 無良業主！擺食！","createTime":"2020-06-11T08:37:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T09:14:05.000Z","uid":166254,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f9c2d1502a4b613df4c92a92a911ab066551c72f","tid":2059873,"uid":166254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T08:37:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/seiKobH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FseiKobH.jpg&h=38ffacbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日經過大圍去探朋友，個朋友係其中一間鋪位嘅租客，點之見到哩間比人停水停電，就問朋友咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來疫情期間業主冇減租減電費，email一律唔覆，哩間冇錢比租金，所以比人停水停電，按金仲要冇撚左！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加德士石油老闆 無 良 藍 絲 ！ 呢鋪真係要擺食<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推爆佢！！</span>"},{"pid":"1f6aa8be92422f0d8f9d35b21c443cd27cd13975","tid":2059873,"uid":166254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T08:58:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0395838cc76a684552079cb5e883111971929e01","tid":2059873,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T09:00:55.000Z","msg":"唔明"},{"pid":"aeceb5187a3740d800e1ec2fcce8eee65da50164","tid":2059873,"uid":33326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T09:01:46.000Z","msg":"唔明"},{"pid":"a243c27715dd33aaaddf64dc2642879752cc1886","tid":2059873,"uid":166254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T09:07:17.000Z","msg":"大圍揾食巿集！！！ 登我朋友唔扺"},{"pid":"66c4542c10b847bd5ca0e03bca0fbe6ca841276f","tid":2059873,"uid":272424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T09:10:49.000Z","msg":"你講減嗰啲係人情唔減係道理啦<br />\n要講就講入面寫業主咩唔還裝修按金嗰樣嘢"},{"pid":"4c0ab49efa1c3642852b9a78aca481a76887ed06","tid":2059873,"uid":272424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":